766
00:49:46,775 --> 00:49:47,775
Menyeberang!

767
00:50:00,206 --> 00:50:01,207
Bagus!

768
00:50:01,707 --> 00:50:02,708
Mereka mundur!

769
00:50:32,947 --> 00:50:33,947
Tunggu.

770
00:50:38,244 --> 00:50:40,746
