797
00:52:04,830 --> 00:52:06,665
Katamu, frekuensinya terbuka.

798
00:52:07,458 --> 00:52:09,585
Bagaimana jika didengar pihak lain?

799
00:52:09,668 --> 00:52:12,588
Kau mau kita luntang-lantung di udara?

