00:52:16,175 --> 00:52:21,639
Pertaruhan harga diri pengendali elite
Korea Selatan dan Korea Utara…

801
00:52:23,265 --> 00:52:24,892
Ternyata lebih sederhana.

802
00:52:24,975 --> 00:52:26,018
Tidak.

803
00:52:27,186 --> 00:52:28,186
