00:54:00,529 --> 00:54:02,281
Aku mendengarkan. Bicaralah.

815
00:54:16,253 --> 00:54:18,547
<i>Selesai memadamkan kebakaran hutan.</i>

816
00:54:18,630 --> 00:54:20,215
